node.text: I thought I’d share a quote from Rainer Maria Rilke..It lives within my character Anthony in @nbccouncilofdads and it now lives with me: “Be patient toward all that is unsolved in your heart and try to love the questions themselves, like locked rooms and like books that are now written in a very foreign tongue. Do not now seek the answers, which cannot be given you because you would not be able to live them. And the point is, to live everything. Live the questions now. Perhaps you will then gradually, without noticing it, live along some distant day into the answer.”
Thanks @koi.pondering for this beautiful art work! Amazing!
